  "body": "**Only happens against the call-trace branch**\r\n\r\nThis curl command:\r\n\r\n```[bash]\r\ncurl -s --location --request POST --header 'Content-Type:  application/json' --data-raw '{\"jsonrpc\":  \"2.0\",\"method\":  \"trace_transaction\",\"params\":  [\"0x88162c6bcbb040fd8f6676fe336f83d7a27a5765b18bfce524beea2a0e107159\"],\"id\":  \"1\"}' http://localhost:8545\r\n```\r\n\r\nreturns:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"error\": {\r\n    \"code\": -32000,\r\n    \"message\": \"method handler crashed\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"id\": \"1\",\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error occurs in this code block: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/blob/trace-call/cmd/rpcdaemon/commands/trace_types.go#L181\r\n\r\n",
